Vincent Kartheiser https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Vincent_Kartheiser 0 Vincent Paul Kartheiser (born May 5, 1979) is an American actor. He is best known for his roles as Connor on The WB television series Angel and as Pete Campbell on the AMC television series Mad Men, for which he received six Screen Actors Guild Award nominations for Outstanding Performance by an Ensemble in a Drama Series and won twice along with the cast.
